Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.04,0:00:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what about that person?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.74,0:00:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, where?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.84,0:00:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.04,0:00:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, he's cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.84,0:00:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Told you the boys in university are in a league of their own.{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.24,0:00:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.44,0:00:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That cockscomb is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.18,0:01:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that really what you'd call your type?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.48,0:01:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.96,0:01:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you thinking of, you two?!{g} \NWe're here for a meeting with friends, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.88,0:01:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go there quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.18,0:01:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, sure, very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.08,0:01:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, sis, you just don't know when to stop. {no clue what she means by "endless; never-ending; going on forever"}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.54,0:01:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, this part of school \Nfeels so lonely...{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.38,0:01:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.11,0:01:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what is this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.47,0:01:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You no longer know where we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.29,0:01:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the pamphlet doesn't mention \Nanything of the kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.82,0:01:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.13,0:01:37.59,Sign,,0,0,0,,Mahjong club {麻雀同好会}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.86,0:01:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a mahjong club! {麻雀同好会}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.52,0:01:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.88,0:01:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go ask there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.49,0:01:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But it looks kinda creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.05,0:01:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no such place \Nmentioned anywhere in the pamphlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.11,0:01:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever! Let's go, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.27,0:01:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, excuse us?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.77,0:01:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is anyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.06,0:01:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.03,0:01:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like nobody's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.52,0:01:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This room makes me uneasy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.12,0:02:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's ask somewhere else!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.38,0:02:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I help you with? {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.38,0:02:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My! Such a cute Rabbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.33,0:02:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like we got lost in the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.09,0:02:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We're looking for our friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.78,0:02:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's good, that's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.38,0:02:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way, young ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.01,0:02:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone of you plays mahjong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.30,0:02:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we do play it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.95,0:02:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's this about? {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.26,0:02:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Young ladies, wouldn't you like \Nto join me for a game or two?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.94,0:02:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.19,0:02:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, come on, come on! \NGo ahead and take a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.81,0:02:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't push me! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of creature are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.78,0:02:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Good thing you asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Before you - the Great Mahjong King Ravijan! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get to see with your own eyes \Njust how far my mahjong prowess spans! {no clue what he means by "show with far" I dont suppose he actually means watch from afar}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.38,0:02:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The king of mahjong, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.51,0:02:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.06,0:02:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Show us how far your prowess spans.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.05,0:02:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,W-W-What's with this unconcerned attitude? {/composure}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:03:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,1500)}Well, it won't stay this way for long! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.47,0:03:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take it easy on you at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.38,0:03:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.81,0:03:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! That's a ron!{no clue, I have exactly 0 knowledge of mahjong}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I got riichi on my first try and was waiting for a dora! {same, hereafter too}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.73,0:03:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about time I got serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.49,0:03:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.03,0:03:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I got this one. Pure straight dora dora. {pure straight; winning hand containing nine consecutive tiles of the same suit (i.e. 1-9)​}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.79,0:03:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonsense! Nonsense! That's a load of nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.08,0:03:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Blessing of earth with thirteen orphans! {blessing of earth; winning with a self-drawn tile in the first turn​}{hammi: Not black suit, it's the hand kokushi musou/thirteen orphans, so a double/possibly triple yakuman hand}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.30,0:03:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.51,0:03:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen it, Rabbit? {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in luck today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.79,0:03:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! I-It's has to be a mistake! {mistakenly announcing a win without having all the requisite tiles​ - marked as obsolete but I don't see how the unobsolete meaning may make sense: unintentional rule violation accompanied by a penalty}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,When the three are declaring victory all at once, \Nobviously, someone is mistaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.98,0:03:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I, the mahjong king, \Nwould lose to a bunch of little girls like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.01,0:03:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You better take that back about the little girls! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.15,0:04:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think we three are?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In the game of mahjong, \Nthere are no passers-by. {hope she means this, "no one you encounter in mj is random stranger"}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.00,0:04:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,W-W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.67,0:04:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.24,0:04:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We are the Three Super Real Mahjong Maidens!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.87,0:04:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Come again after you've trained for some more! {/sharpen your skill and try again}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.96,0:04:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,N-N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.30,0:04:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.59,0:04:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he go cray-cray from losing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! So you were {\i1}those{\i0} three maidens all along!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.81,0:04:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.04,0:04:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.26,0:04:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The grudge of all men who lost to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.79,0:04:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Will return right back at you! {no clue, first word is kinda like omoishiru but what does he mean by I'll make you realize? assumed "I'll make you feel"; no clue what's last word}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.45,0:04:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.38,0:04:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.38,0:04:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
