Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:05:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.89,0:05:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did they come from?{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.27,0:05:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Such outlandish looks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.41,0:06:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Who gave you the idea to sleep in place like this? {actually "you'll catch a cold" but man that sounds trite as fuck}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! What are you doing? {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You came to your senses?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.18,0:06:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What kind of place is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You are in the town of Pinfu. {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Town of Pinfu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.54,0:06:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, where did you guys come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right. We suddenly fell into a strange hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy named Ravijan... {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh! Don't you let that name \Nfly carelessly off your lips here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.81,0:06:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But boy, you won't get far, looking like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.55,0:06:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, what happened? {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.02,0:06:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H261053&}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.86,0:06:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You girls wanna buy some clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.93,0:06:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But we've no money with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.09,0:06:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty sure you do! Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? T-This?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.85,0:06:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, look! The real tiles! {assumed janpai}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.27,0:06:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasumi, where'd you get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:06:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems I unconsciously grabbed them as I fell. {no clue what to make of 夢中} {/when we fell, I was holding onto them in muchuu}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.79,0:07:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as they say!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.84,0:07:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A drowning man will clutch at a mahjong tile!​
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.70,0:07:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm unimpressed. {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.63,0:07:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How absurd. {g as well}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.67,0:07:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.38,0:07:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You can eat at my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.19,0:07:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,With that much money, you'll get a hefty change \Neven after buying new clothes and a dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we really? {meaning you'll let us into your house?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.61,0:07:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I live with my grandpa, \Nthe place is a little shabby, but please don't be shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.12,0:07:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Our house is right past this street. {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.11,0:07:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ravijan - what kind of thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.38,0:07:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.48,0:07:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.73,0:07:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.38,0:07:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They're playing mahjong with paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there too! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.72,0:07:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. They're using paper tiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.95,0:07:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,In retaliation for losing a mahjong bout, \Nthat rabbit monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,took away every single mahjong tile in the country!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.80,0:07:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why the real tiles are so valuable?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.22,0:08:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That miscreant rabbit Ravijan... {/monster }
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.86,0:08:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.07,0:08:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A Peeping Cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.74,0:08:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hide!{/dangerous}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hide somewhere, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.56,0:08:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The damnation! This is {\i1}his{\i0} doing as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He appointed the Peeping Cat to monitor the city, \Noccasionally summoning a tornado like this! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He does it to take the fun of playing mahjong \Naway from the people of this town!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.92,0:08:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What a vile guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.91,0:08:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All because he's such a mahjong softie! {actually "despite being weak in mahjong"}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.87,0:08:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna be flying in the sky, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Shoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.57,0:08:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, so Ravijan did that to you? {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.51,0:09:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you tell us what kind of thing Ravijan is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.24,0:09:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.30,0:09:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, he just suddenly came to this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.51,0:09:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody knows what kind of thing he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.14,0:09:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He smells like something \Nthat belongs to another world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.60,0:09:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So he is not from this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa is an old-school fortune-teller. {/Grandpa is the master of the old school technique.} {tlc, no clue whatsoever, assumed "reisen 術師(technique user)" but no clue what's reisen; actually line on 9:53 reveals he's a fortune teller so this probably "rei senjutsu(divination; fortune-telling; mantic) shi(master)"}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.29,0:09:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy is using the most dubious techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.52,0:09:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Keeps doing away mercilessly \Nwith those who don't comply. {/kills those who don't align with his wishes/designs}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,With the mahjong tiles he took away from the people{ of the whole country},
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.09,0:09:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,he built a fortress off the coast, \Nfrom which he rules over all of our country.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Among the people of our country, \Nevery single one loves and enjoys mahjong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So we worked hard to nurture and fertilize it \Nas something that'll give us strength tomorrow. {nourishment (mental, spiritual, etc.); sustenance (e.g. of one's life); source of encouragement}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.20,0:09:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Such was the country we had once, rich and beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.53,0:09:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And now that country...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.33,0:09:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.63,0:09:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea where is the entrance \Nto another world that those three came from?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.47,0:09:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you want to know that? {}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! You'll teach us how to find our way back?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.41,0:09:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Grandpa's divination never misses the mark! {now}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu, get everything ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.50,0:10:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.60,0:10:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.41,0:10:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.48,0:10:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,In the middle of Ravijan's fortress!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.84,0:10:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! What ill fortune...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa, hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,With that knowledge, we'll return home...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.06,0:10:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,In no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.98,0:10:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.05,0:10:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the evil's nest ran by Ravijan, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.89,0:10:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you even understand what that means?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.14,0:10:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:11:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,When we get to that bunny...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.11,0:11:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll beat him! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.62,0:11:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And return to our own world!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.38,0:11:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa, do you suppose that those three \Ncould defeat Ravijan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. Yu, please bring the Scoring Stick Saber. {scoring stick; counter; chip​}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.13,0:11:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Scoring Stick Saber?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.80,0:11:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. A long time ago, \Nin order to defeat Ravijan,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the townspeople joined forces and manufactured this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.54,0:11:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.30,0:11:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a scoring stick?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.32,0:11:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.01,0:11:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected, when wielded by someone courageous, \Nit lets them project a great power with it. {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.56,0:11:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. The young men who stood up to face Ravijan a long time ago also possessed infinite courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.03,0:11:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, the power of his magic is also tremendous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.24,0:11:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you lose your courage, \Nthe Scoring Stick Saber also becomes useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Just thinking about all the young men \Nwho lost their lives fighting him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.29,0:11:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, go there and defeat Ravijan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,None of us here can wield those sabers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:11:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the chosen ones, the heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.43,0:12:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Use those sabers to defeat Ravijan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Avenge all the fallen townspeople!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Avenge father for me, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.47,0:12:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.74,0:12:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.20,0:12:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My son, the father of my granddaughter \Nstood up against Ravijan and lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll make sure to...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.56,0:12:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Defeat Ravijan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And restore peace in this world!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.54,0:12:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We're off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:43.59,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.87,0:12:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for taking care of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.58,0:12:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care and watch your step.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.39,0:12:47.00,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take this as a farewell gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:53.85,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.06,0:12:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.11,0:12:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.19,0:12:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.89,0:12:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You use it when you're in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:57.80,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:12:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.68,0:13:01.78,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.61,0:13:08.16,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If you run into trouble, come again anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.29,0:13:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Yu. {no clue, this yuyo can be her full name?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.54,0:13:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... What is it, Grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.84,0:13:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think those three can actually defeat Ravijan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:17.63,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.33,0:13:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,When the three that get along so well join forces,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:25.78,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.34,0:13:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.04,0:13:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so clumsy, sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.04,0:13:30.58,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.22,0:13:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What now? It was Shoko who stumbled!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It was because Kasumi was appreciating the view! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.85,0:13:34.06,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.32,0:13:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No I wasn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.48,0:13:41.30,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.77,0:13:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hurry up and get off me! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.58,0:13:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all? Those cats are too weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Off to a good start! {}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.53,0:13:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.91,0:13:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the way! {}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.45,0:13:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Weak! {}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:13:59.83,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.79,0:14:03.45,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.78,0:14:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? The cat turned into a mahjong tile!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.71,0:14:10.51,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.48,0:14:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.38,0:14:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.59,0:14:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,These cats are just mahjong tiles \Nthat Ravijan cast a spell on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.68,0:14:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.05,0:14:14.29,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.31,0:14:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.28,0:14:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that means everything here \Nis made of tiles, right? {no clue what she means}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.47,0:14:17.94,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.88,0:14:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.48,0:14:24.80,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.52,0:14:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.64,0:14:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit them with the Scoring Sticks! {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.11,0:14:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be the richest people around!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.65,0:14:33.12,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, come right in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:42.34,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.44,0:14:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Get in the bag! Oh! Here too! Ah! Here too! \NHere too! Here too! Here too! Here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.84,0:14:47.51,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.85,0:14:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, Kasumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.50,0:14:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You fight them too, not just gather the tiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.26,0:14:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing how well you manage it, \NI'd rather cheer you on. {no clue what's waite, prolly "湧く" but still no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.47,0:14:50.68,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...{}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.19,0:14:57.81,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.00,0:14:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like we got rid of the most of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I also collected so much money!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.81,0:15:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing! It enough to live like queens \Nfor the rest of our lives! {/play around/have fun}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to live here for the rest of your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.25,0:15:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still more?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.18,0:15:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let him escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.61,0:15:11.37,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:14.39,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.39,0:15:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.50,0:15:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Curl, curl, curl... {no clue but later he summons a tornado}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.99,0:15:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened again!{nc}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.39,0:15:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take it anymore! It hurts!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.08,0:15:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.55,0:16:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Um. I'm sorry if you find my directness inappropriate, but I got bird food here. {}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to buy some?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:12.13,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.76,0:16:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Bird food. Would you like some?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.13,0:16:17.46,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.46,0:16:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:28.86,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.06,0:16:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Bird food! Would you like to buy some bird food?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:30.48,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.70,0:16:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give us that sparkling smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.28,0:16:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,She's catching up!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:37.41,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.99,0:16:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Bird food! Would you like some...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.29,0:16:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.78,0:16:41.54,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.67,0:16:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! Now's our chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.09,0:16:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,To run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.83,0:16:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But now I feel a bit sorry for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:47.71,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.07,0:16:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.75,0:16:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll buy your bird food.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.75,0:16:59.81,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.72,0:16:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.67,0:16:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.66,0:16:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! It's just 40 tiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.43,0:16:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Consumption tax and basket are included as service.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.01,0:16:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, I could also give you a loan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.79,0:17:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Loans are available in 6 to 12 installments, \Nstarting at 7 tiles per month. {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:10.77,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.27,0:17:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's way too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A loan for the bird food?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.80,0:17:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody would pay 40 tiles for that!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.77,0:17:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.77,0:17:16.99,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.99,0:17:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Until I... Until I sell all of it, I can't return home!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.99,0:17:21.83,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.20,0:17:23.05,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.48,0:17:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A-All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.15,0:17:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll buy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.17,0:17:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.48,0:17:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, why'd you make a purchase like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.85,0:17:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.39,0:17:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How unfriendly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.36,0:17:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Those statues look so unfriendly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh, you're annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Who made such senseless things?{}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Just forget it and start walking!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.39,0:17:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There! Sis, isn't it cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.39,0:17:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stay here if you want! {no clue what she means, assumed "do it for the rest of your life"}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.77,0:18:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make it into a work of art.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.12,0:18:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's add some lipstick next.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.66,0:18:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.78,0:18:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ravijan's magic again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use! They're too nimble, I can't catch any!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.55,0:18:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Kasumi?
